trans-unit.source: Specifies properties and patterns that the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] framework caches when an <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement"></xref> is obtained.
trans-unit.target: Anger egenskaper och mönster som den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] framework cachelagrar när en <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement"> </xref> hämtas.

trans-unit.source: Retrieving properties and patterns through [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] requires cross-process calls that can slow down performance.
trans-unit.target: Hämta egenskaper och mönster via [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] kräver mellan olika processer-anrop som kan långsammare prestanda.

trans-unit.source: By caching values of proprieties and patterns in a batch operation, you can enhance the performance of your application.
trans-unit.target: Du kan förbättra prestanda för ditt program cachelagrar värdena för proprieties och mönster i en batchåtgärd.

trans-unit.source: Create a new cache request by calling the class constructor.
trans-unit.target: Skapa en ny cachebegäran om genom att anropa klasskonstruktorn.

trans-unit.source: The request is populated by repeated calls to the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Add%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Begäran innehåller upprepade anrop till den <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Add%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Add%2A>

trans-unit.source: Only a single CacheRequest can be active.
trans-unit.target: Endast en enskild CacheRequest kan vara aktiv.

trans-unit.source: There are two ways to activate a request: - Call <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Activate%2A> on the request.
trans-unit.target: Det finns två sätt att aktivera en begäran:-anropa <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Activate%2A>på begäran.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Activate%2A>

trans-unit.source: This pushes the request onto the stack, and the request is popped when the object is disposed.
trans-unit.target: Detta skickar en begäran till stacken och begäran popup när objektet har tagits bort.

trans-unit.source: To ensure disposal even if an exception is raised, use the return value from <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Activate%2A> within a `using` block (`Using` in [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_visualbnet](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-visualbnet-md.md)]).
trans-unit.target: Använd returvärde från för att säkerställa avyttring även om ett undantagsfel genereras, <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Activate%2A>inom en `using` block (`Using` i [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_visualbnet](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-visualbnet-md.md)]).</xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Activate%2A>

trans-unit.source: - Put the request onto the internal stack by calling <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Push%2A>.
trans-unit.target: -Placera begäran till interna stacken genom att anropa <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Push%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Push%2A>

trans-unit.source: Only the topmost request on the stack is active, and it must be the next one removed from the stack by <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Pop%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Endast de översta begäranden på stacken är aktiv, och den måste vara den nästa som tas bort från stacken med <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Pop%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Pop%2A>

trans-unit.source: Popping the request deactivates it.
trans-unit.target: Inaktiverar den poppar begäran.

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] elements obtained while the request is active will have cached values for the properties and patterns specified.
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)]element som hämtades när begäran är aktiv kommer värden för egenskaper och mönster som angetts cachelagras.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: When a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest> is created, the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.RuntimeIdProperty> identifier is added as a default property to cache.
trans-unit.target: När en <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest>har skapats kan den <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.RuntimeIdProperty>identifierare läggs till som en default-egenskap till cachen.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.RuntimeIdProperty> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest>

trans-unit.source: Sets this <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest"></xref> as the active specification for the items that are returned when an <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement"></xref> is requested on the same thread.
trans-unit.target: Anger det <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest"> </xref> som aktiv specifikationen för de objekt som returneras när ett <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement"> </xref> begärs på samma tråd.

trans-unit.source: Using this method is usually preferable to using <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Push%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Pop%2A> as a means of activating the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest>.
trans-unit.target: Med den här metoden är vanligtvis bättre att använda <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Push%2A>och <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Pop%2A>för att aktivera <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Pop%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Push%2A>

trans-unit.source: The object is pushed onto the stack when Activate is called, and then popped off when it is disposed.
trans-unit.target: Objektet pushas till stacken när aktivera kallas och sedan bort från när den har tagits bort.

trans-unit.source: To ensure disposal, place the return value within a `using` block (`Using` in [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_visualbnet](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-visualbnet-md.md)]).
trans-unit.target: För att säkerställa avyttring, placera det returnera värdet inom en `using` block (`Using` i [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_visualbnet](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-visualbnet-md.md)]).

trans-unit.source: The object that can be used to dispose the <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Det objekt som kan användas för att ta bort den <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.AutomationPattern"></xref> identifier to this <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Lägger till den angivna <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.AutomationPattern"> </xref> identifierare till den här <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Adding a pattern that is already in the cache request has no effect.
trans-unit.target: Lägga till ett mönster som redan finns i cachebegäran har ingen effekt.

trans-unit.source: An identifier specifying a pattern to cache.
trans-unit.target: En identifierare som anger ett mönster som ska cachelagras.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest"></xref> is active.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest"> </xref> är aktiv.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.AutomationProperty"></xref> identifier to this <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Lägger till den angivna <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.AutomationProperty"> </xref> identifierare till den här <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: When a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest> is created, the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.RuntimeIdProperty> identifier is added as a default property to cache.
trans-unit.target: När en <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest>har skapats kan den <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.RuntimeIdProperty>identifierare läggs till som en default-egenskap till cachen.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.RuntimeIdProperty> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest>

trans-unit.source: Adding a property that is already in the cache request has no effect.
trans-unit.target: Lägga till en egenskap som är redan i cachebegäran har ingen effekt.

trans-unit.source: An identifier specifying a property value to cache.
trans-unit.target: En identifierare som anger ett värde för egenskapen till cachen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest"></xref> is active.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest"> </xref> är aktiv.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that specifies whether returned elements should contain full references to the underlying [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)], or only cached information.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger ett värde som anger om returnerade element får innehålla fullständiga referenser till den underliggande [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)], eller endast cachelagrad information.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode> is the default value, and specifies that returned elements contain a full reference to the underlying [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode>är standardvärdet och anger att returnerade element innehåller en fullständig referens till den underliggande [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].</xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode> specifies that the returned elements have no reference to the underlying [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], and contain only cached information.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode>Anger att de returnerade element har ingen referens till den underliggande [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], och innehåller endast cachelagrad information.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode>

trans-unit.source: Certain operations on elements, including <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCurrentPropertyValue%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCurrentPattern%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.SetFocus%2A>, require a full reference; attempting to perform these on an element that has none results in an <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>.
trans-unit.target: Vissa åtgärder på element, inklusive <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCurrentPropertyValue%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCurrentPattern%2A>, och <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.SetFocus%2A>, kräver en fullständig referens; vid försök att utföra dessa på ett element som ingen har resulterar i en <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>.</xref:System.InvalidOperationException> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.SetFocus%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCurrentPattern%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCurrentPropertyValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: Using <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode> can be more efficient when only properties are needed, as it avoids the overhead involved in setting up full references.
trans-unit.target: Med hjälp av <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode>kan vara mer effektivt när det behövs endast egenskaper, som den slipper som är involverad i att konfigurera fullständiga referenser.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode>

trans-unit.source: <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode"></xref> if the returned elements have a full reference to the underlying [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)]; otherwise <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode"></xref>Om de returnerade element har en fullständig referens till den underliggande [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)], annars <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Creates a copy of this <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Skapar en kopia av detta <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A modifiable copy of the current object.
trans-unit.target: En ändringsbar kopia av det aktuella objektet.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest"></xref> that is active on the current thread.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar den <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest"> </xref> som är aktiv på den aktuella tråden.

trans-unit.source: The active <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Aktivt <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Removes the active <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest"></xref> from the internal stack for the current thread.
trans-unit.target: Tar bort aktivt <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest"> </xref> från interna stacken för den aktuella tråden.

trans-unit.source: Only the currently active request can be removed using the Pop method.
trans-unit.target: Endast aktiva begäran kan tas bort med metoden Pop.

trans-unit.source: Attempting to remove a request that is not the current one results in an exception.
trans-unit.target: Försök att ta bort en begäran är inte aktuell en resultatet i ett undantag.

trans-unit.source: Unless you are nesting cache requests, it is preferable to use <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Activate%2A> to place the request on the stack.
trans-unit.target: Om du för många kapslade cachebegäranden, är det bättre att använda <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Activate%2A>att placera begäran på stacken.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Activate%2A>

trans-unit.source: The reason is that you can use <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Activate%2A> within a `using` block (`Using` in [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_visualbnet](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-visualbnet-md.md)]), ensuring that the request is popped off the stack even if an exception is raised.
trans-unit.target: Det beror på att du kan använda <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Activate%2A>inom en `using` block (`Using` i [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_visualbnet](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-visualbnet-md.md)]), se till att begäran bort från stacken även om ett undantagsfel genereras.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Activate%2A>

trans-unit.source: An attempt was made to remove a cache request that was not the last one pushed onto the stack.
trans-unit.target: Ett försök gjordes att ta bort en cachebegäran som inte var det sista pushas till stacken.

trans-unit.source: Places the <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest"></xref> on the internal state stack, making it the active request on the current thread.
trans-unit.target: Platser i <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest"> </xref> i det interna tillståndet-stacken, vilket gör det aktiva begäran på den aktuella tråden.

trans-unit.source: Multiple <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest> objects can be placed onto the state stack.
trans-unit.target: Flera <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest>objekt kan placeras till stacken tillstånd.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest>

trans-unit.source: Cache requests must be removed from the stack in the order they were pushed on; otherwise, an <xref:System.InvalidOperationException> exception is raised.
trans-unit.target: Cache-begäranden måste tas bort från stacken i den ordning som de har vidare. Annars en <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>undantagsfel genereras.</xref:System.InvalidOperationException>

trans-unit.source: Unless you are nesting cache requests, it is preferable to use <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Activate%2A> to place the request on the stack.
trans-unit.target: Om du för många kapslade cachebegäranden, är det bättre att använda <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Activate%2A>att placera begäran på stacken.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Activate%2A>

trans-unit.source: The reason is that you can use <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Activate%2A> within a `using` block (`Using` in [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_visualbnet](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-visualbnet-md.md)]), ensuring that the request is popped off the stack even if an exception is raised.
trans-unit.target: Det beror på att du kan använda <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Activate%2A>inom en `using` block (`Using` i [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_visualbnet](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-visualbnet-md.md)]), se till att begäran bort från stacken även om ett undantagsfel genereras.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest.Activate%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value specifying the view of the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] element tree to use when caching.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger ett värde som anger vyn i den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] element trädet ska användas när cachelagring.

trans-unit.source: For additional information on views of the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] element tree, see [UI Automation Tree Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: För ytterligare information om av den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] element trädet finns [UI Automation trädet översikt](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: The view of the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] element tree.
trans-unit.target: Vyn i den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] element trädet.

trans-unit.source: The default view is <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Automation.ControlViewCondition"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standardvyn är <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Automation.ControlViewCondition"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that specifies whether caching is done only for the root of the subtree, or also for its children or descendants.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger ett värde som anger om cachelagring görs endast för underträdet roten eller också för dess underordnade eller underordnade.

trans-unit.source: The scope of caching is in relation to the object or objects being fetched, not in relation to the object on which <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.FindFirst%2A> or <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.FindAll%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: Omfånget för cachelagring i förhållande till det eller de objekt som ska hämtas, inte i förhållande till objektet som <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.FindFirst%2A>eller <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.FindAll%2A>kallas.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.FindAll%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.FindFirst%2A>

trans-unit.source: See the example.
trans-unit.target: Se exemplet.

trans-unit.source: One or more of <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.TreeScope"></xref>, <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.TreeScope"></xref>, <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.TreeScope"></xref>, or <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.TreeScope"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: One or more of <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.TreeScope"></xref>, <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.TreeScope"></xref>, <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.TreeScope"></xref>, or <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.TreeScope"></xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default value is <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.TreeScope"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standardvärdet är <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.TreeScope"> </xref>.

trans-unit.target: Ett försök gjordes att ange egenskapen till <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.TreeScope"> </xref> eller <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.TreeScope"> </xref>.
